text: Had haircut in last three years here. Rly good even I am not living in London and I was always coming to London to do haircut in this store. But sometimes the time to wait is a bit long

(Translated by Google) The cut is not bad, the wash and blow is only 17 pounds.

(Original)
剪的还不错洗剪吹才17磅
Went there a few times for a haircut it was ok but the last time it was absolutely horrendous.
